<br>
But when you are SOLOING IT sucks canal water BIG TIME!!!!<br>
<br>
In 35, so far I have died at LEAST 3 times to LD. <br>
<br>
<br>
Examples,,,<br>
<br>
In NK, less than 10 peeps in zone, a farmer yells about the swarm coming. I look at track and what to I see, the Swarm Mother!! I chase her down, she is yellow to me, I land a good snare on her, and I pull her away from the swarmlings SOLO!!!<br>
Weeee haaaaa! I drag her out into nowhere, root her, drop 2 dots on her, sit and med, root breaks and I repeat this dance about 4 times over 10 minutes till ensnare runs off and she is less than a buble of health left. I stand up, resnare her, when I get the &quot;you have been diconnected&quot; message.. ARRRRGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGG!G!!!!!! By the time I can log back in, I am nekkid in Thurgadin.<br>
<br>
In Rath Mountains, this time with my Shammy friend, I am in Wolfform pulling giants. I run up the hill, pull one with a small spell as to not hold too much aggro, turn and run all the way back to my friend near the Lizard Camp. As I get to my friend, I noteing my lag bar is a 80% and climbing. JUST as I was to go LD, it returns to normal long enough for me to see,,<br>
A hill giant hits you for tremendous damage...<br>
A hill giant hits you for tremendous damage...<br>
A hill giant hits you for tremendous damage...<br>
A hill giant hits you for tremendous damage...<br>
A hill giant hits you for tremendous damage...<br>
A hill giant hits you for tremendous damage...<br>
Loading please wait...<br>
And a top down view of me dead.<br>
When I finally found my corpse, I was laying right where I casted my initial spell. I never moved. I never hit auto attack.<br>
<br>
Now, I understand why the code is the way it is, to stop folks from pulling the plug on their modem when a fight looked hopeless, but jeezzz Lew-ezzzze, when you are FULL HEALTH and AUTO ATTACK is OFF and you are LD, should that NOT be an indication that your not trying to beat the system???!?!!!!!!! <br>
<br>
Why let the mob eat us up when we can not fight back????<br>
<br>
At least LET ME LOG BACK IN so I can fight the dam thing!<br>
<br>
At least turn on my auto attack! OR GATE ME back to my bind point!!!<br>
<br>
Nothing stinks more than being shut out for a few minutes when you KNOW you can get back in and gate away...<br>
<br>
But just letting my LD self stand there and get eaten alive is just wrong, I am sorry.<br>
